# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Starving Artist — environment variables
#
# Good news: this app is zero-config. On Vercel you don't set ANY of these by
# hand — connecting a Neon/Postgres store injects DATABASE_URL automatically,
# and the app generates its own session secret + tables on first run.
#
# For LOCAL dev, the only one you need is DATABASE_URL.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Database (required) ---
# Injected automatically by the Vercel Postgres/Neon integration. Set by hand
# only for local development (a free Neon database works great).
# DATABASE_URL=postgres://user:pass@host/db?sslmode=require

# --- Image uploads (optional) ---
# Injected automatically when you add a Vercel Blob store. Without it, the app
# still works — drops just won't have photos.
# BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=

# --- Session signing secret (optional) ---
# Auto-generated and stored in the DB if unset. Set it only if you want to pin
# a specific value (e.g. `openssl rand -hex 32`).
# SESSION_SECRET=

# --- Serve under a path on ciamac.com (optional) ---
# Set to "/starving-artist" for ciamac.com/starving-artist. Leave unset for a
# subdomain like eats.ciamac.com.
# BASE_PATH=/starving-artist
